<Content>Good Deal for the Money I had low expectations for the hotel because of some of the reviews I had read, however, I found the hotel very decent. It was close the airport and one of the closer hotels to the Messe Sud (convention center). I was attending a conference there, so it was perfect. It was also a short walk to the subway station.All together, it was perfect for a business traveler. The room service left something to be desired, but the breakfast in the morning was good. 
