<Content>Not up to its rating I was rather disappointed by this hotel. Despite its 4-star rating and ambience - lots of glass everywhere - there were several flaws.The rooms had white curtains - a simple mistake that means waking with sunrise - very annoying. The rooms were not very comfortable. The staff were not very friendly, and seemed very stressed. And the breakfasts, although initially appearing to be well appointed, were actually quite limited.You can do a lot worse than this hotel, but you can also do a lot better.As regards location, you're fairly near the airport, but not near anythign else of use. About five minutes away from Rohrdamm U-Bahn station, which can get you into town in about 20-30 minutes. 
